                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6422" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8592 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">寒冬之下，谁在逆流而上：碧水源的混改路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Under the cold winter, who is going upstream:The mixed-ownership reform road of OriginWater</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘思含</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京碧水源科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合所有制改革；民营企业；公司治理结构；投融资</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mixed-ownership reform; Private enterprise; Corporate governance; Investment and financing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国混合所有制改革进入了深水区，除了一直关注的“民混国”的单向改制，市场也逐渐将目光转移到“国混民”的混合所有制改制方向上来。尤其是在近年来的环保市场上，受PPP项目的影响，越来越多的民营企业投入国有企业的怀抱，反向混改的趋势越发明显。本案例旨在通过对碧水源在引入中交集团的起因，过程和结果的描述，引导学生学习和掌握民营企业当前所面临的融资难的问题，以及国有资本在民营企业混改中发挥的效果，同时希望学员能思考和讨论国有企业的加入会对民营企业造成什么风险点以及相应的应对措施，从而能为民营企业是不是应该推进“逆向混改”这一要点问题提供一定程度的借鉴，促进国民经济融合，推动我国经济社会的进一步发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> The importance of mixed-ownership reform has been highly emphasised in China nowadays. In addition to the market focus on the &quot;State-owned enterprises introduce private capital&quot;one-way reform, &quot;Private enterprises introduce state-owned capital &quot;is also an important way to achieve mixed-ownership. Especially in the environmental protection market in recent years, A lots of private enterprises introduce state-owned capital due to the influence of PPP projects, and the trend of reverse mixed-ownership reform has become more significant. This article illustrates the causes, process and results of Beijing OriginWater Technology Co., Ltd. introduce China Communications Construction Company, to guide students to learn and understand the current problems faced by private enterprises in financing, as well as the effect of state-owned capital in the mixed reform of private enterprises, while hoping that students can think about and discuss what risk the entry of state-owned enterprises will cause to private enterprises and the corresponding countermeasures. Thus, it provides some evidences for the key issue of whether private enterprises should conduct mixed-ownership reform, improves national and private integration and promotes economic and social development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息不对称；股权质押风险；混合所有制改革；公司治理；信号传递理论；协同效应；公司治理；过度投资行为</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-08</td>
                            </tr>
